item.title: CVE-2020-36524|2024-08-04T17:30:08.129Z -- unspecified -- refined%20toolkit
item.description: A vulnerability was found in Refined Toolkit. It has been rated as problematic. Affected by this issue is some unknown functionality of the component UI-Image/UI-Button. The manipulation leads to cross site scripting. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
